profile:
Locally owned and operated Granite fabrication and installation shop.

Specialize in granite counter tops, vanities, fireplace surrounds and mantels, threshholds, soap boxs, and really anything you can imagine.. we can make.

Marble, quartz and soapstone are also available for installation.

We pride ourselves on honesty, integridy, and customer satisfaction.
service_area: Belleville, Picton, Cobourg, Tweed and surrounding areas.
payment_method:
cash or cheque.
1/2 down, balance upon installation
